{"id":333476,"type":2,"name":"芒卡环球旅行记","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/2a/fe/333476_Xb1Ax.jpg","summary":"《芒卡环球旅行记》一部奇幻科普动画，是中国最早的一部电视系列动画片，1985年录制，每集15分钟，上海电视台动画制片厂制作。\r\n\r\n森林里一只金丝猴——芒卡既淘气无知又好胜，太阳公公为了帮助老卡学知识，叫小水珠变成云带着芒卡旅行。芒卡一直跟着白云跨洋过洲到达了南极，每到一处，幼稚的芒卡出尽了洋相，引起了许多逗人发笑，也学到了大自然中许多的知识。","info":"<li><span>话数: </span>26</li><li><span>放送开始: </span>1985年6月1日</li><li><span>导演: </span><a href=\"/person/41540\" rel=\"v:directedBy\">陈光明</a>、杨凯华</li><li><span>脚本: </span>奚里德、<a href=\"/person/41540\">陈光明</a>、杨凯华</li><li><span>美术设计: </span><a href=\"/person/41540\">陈光明</a>、杨凯华</li><li><span>播放电视台: </span>上海电视台</li><li><span>其他电视台: </span>北京电视台一套</li><li><span>其他: </span>集数网络上一说为10集</li><li><span>动画设计: </span>张信、赵敏、吴承静、周上泽 等</li><li><span>背景设计: </span>沈勇</li><li><span>动画制作: </span>上海电视台动画制片厂</li><li><span>主题歌作词: </span>茅晓峰</li><li><span>主题歌作曲: </span>姚建婷</li><li><span>主题歌演出: </span>孙佳星</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"eps":[{"id":1023924,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1023924","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"找太阳","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1023925,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1023925","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"深洞遇鼹鼠","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1023926,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1023926","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1023927,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1023927","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1023928,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1023928","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1023929,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1023929","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":1023930,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/1023930","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"